source.name: FMCSA Analysis & Information Online
source.description: The goal of the Analysis and Information (A&I) Online site is to provide information and data to promote analytically sound, safety-conscious decisions by all Motor Carrier Industry stakeholders. The site provides motor carrier safety information including statistical and analytical resources for FMCSA and State enforcement personnel, motor carriers, researchers, insurers, shippers, and the public.
